    Title: Mata Amritanandamayi
    By: Swami Amritasvarupananda
By: Mata Amritanandamayi
Format: verse
---
Creation and Creator art Thou,
Thou art Energy and Truth,
O Goddess, O Goddess, O Goddess!

Creator of the Cosmos art Thou,
And Thou art the beginning and end ...

The Essence of the individual soul art Thou, and
Thou aart the five elements as well ...
